    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price. While the engine and transmission are solid and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows some signs of age, including minor paint oxidation on the roof and a few small dings. The interior is clean but has expected wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a reliable, budget-friendly option for someone who prioritizes mechanical performance over cosmetic perfection.",
