    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including several noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and some minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely need a new set of tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has been maintained regularly but definitely shows its history on the road.",
      "price": 18500.0,
