      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in truly pristine, showroom-level condition. It drives like a total dream and looks like it just rolled off the lot. I've taken such good care of every little detail, and I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It's a total gem\u2014come grab it before it's gone!",
