    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated masterpiece delivers 333 hp at 7,900 RPM, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with precise, short-throw engagement. Power is distributed via a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip through high-lateral-G cornering. The suspension geometry is factory-spec, providing a communicative feedback loop through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this unit shows zero signs of thermal cycling fatigue or fluid seepage. A true collector\u2019s specimen with a comprehensive service dossier and no deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
