    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a 2021 BMW 540i M Sport that looks and feels as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The Alpine White exterior is protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating, showing zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the Mocha Nappa leather remains supple and retains that 'new car' fragrance, with absolutely no creases or wear on the bolsters. Every surface, from the high-gloss wood trim to the digital cockpit, is flawless and free of dust or scratches. Mechanically, it is in peak performance, supported by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at BMW authorized centers. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly museum-grade condition. Includes all original keys, manuals, window sticker, and a custom-fit car cover.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
